text: Yulia Gaufler is a Russian water polo player. She played for the Russian women's national water polo team in the 2006 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2010 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2006 FINA Women's Water Polo World Cup, 2007 World Aquatics Championships, 2009 World Aquatics Championships, and 2011 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Yulia Gaufler getty Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Russian water polo players
